title: Grateful Dead Live at Silva Hall, Hult Center on 1983-08-29
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Minglewood Blues, Friend Of The Devil, Hell In A Bucket, Bird Song, It's All Over Now, Might As Well

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> The Wheel-> The Other One-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Johnny B. Goode, E: U.S. Blues
